                              Linux CLI

Linux
Mudar diretorio = cd
Voltar diretorio = cd ..
Remover pasta = rm -rf
 
 Permissao de pasta 
    Tipos de usuarios 
    user = u
    other= o
    general = g
    -----------------
    add permissao = +
    remove permissao = -

    ex: chmod u+wrx NomePasta  

ls = lima tela 
crl + l = limpa tela
killall -9 NomePorta= mata sessao aberta 
Ctrl + alt + t = abre erminal 
Ctrl + shift + w = fecha o erminal 




 
 

Install NVM

curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/creationix/nvm/v0.33.11/install.sh | bash
command -v nvm
source ~/.bashrc
command -v nvm
nvm install node
nvm ls

Install NODE.JS

curl -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_8.x | sudo bash -
sudo apt install nodejs
node --version

